Package: GEEmediate
Title: Mediation Analysis for Leneralized Linear Models Using the Difference Method
Authors@R: person("Daniel", "Nevo", email = "danielnevo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Causal mediation analysis for a single exposure/treatment and a single mediator, 
  both allowed to be either continuous or binary. The package implements the difference method
  and provide point and interval estimates as well as testing for the natural direct and 
  indirect effects and the mediation proportion.
Version: 0.0.0
Date: 2016-11-09
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports: stats, gee
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: no
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
BugReports: https://github.com/daniel258/GEEMediate/issues
